name: DOA Marie Rose Blue Leotard (TI Embedding)
description:
Finally, my first WORKING ti embedding after so many failures. 😭😭😭

Use akii_marie_rose in prompt to activate and clip_skip=2 preferred. Trained on NAI model but may also work for others.

The examples are generated using Corneo's 7th Heaven Mix (one of my favorite blend😊).
